+# AGENTS.md — SuiteCloud Ventas
+
+Quick-reference for agents working in this repo. See `CLAUDE.md` for full domain docs.
+
+## Build & Test
+
+```bash
+mvn clean compile                     # needs --enable-preview (pom.xml handles it)
+mvn clean package -DskipTests         # full jar
+mvn test -Dtest=TslFrameParserServiceTest#buildTransaction_checkout_oneLineItem
+```
+
+- **Java 25 + `--enable-preview`** — compiled/test/run via pom.xml `<compilerArgs>`. Never remove.
+- **Private Maven repo** at `azdevops1.sipecom.com` — builds fail outside VPN.
+- **Unit tests**: `@ExtendWith(MockitoExtension.class)` — zero Spring context.
+- **Known failure** (don't fix): `XmlGeneratorServiceTest.generate_omitDeclaration_false_hasXmlDeclaration` — Spring XML transformer difference.
+- **Maven wrapper** available (`mvnw.cmd`).
+
+## Architecture non-negotiables
+
+- **Hexagonal layers**: `domain/` has zero framework deps; `infrastructure/` holds all adapters.
+- **Virtual threads**: `spring.threads.virtual.enabled=true` — never use `synchronized`. Use `ReentrantLock`/`Semaphore`.
+- **Domain models**: immutable Java `record`s — mutations return `with*()` copies. Collections wrapped in `List.copyOf()`.
+- **Two datasources**: primary `ARTS_EC` (`datasource`), secondary `DEVS_EC` (`datasource-devs`).
+- **JPA `ddl-auto: none`** — DevTicketEntity cross-database ref (`DEVS_EC.dbo.DV_TICKET`) can't be validated by Hibernate.
+
+## Code style (will be flagged by review)
+
+- Identifiers (classes, methods, vars, packages): **English**.
+- Comments, logs, Javadoc: **Spanish**.
+- Logging: SLF4J 2.0+ fluent API only — `log.atInfo().setMessage("...").addKeyValue("k", v).log()`. Never concatenate into message string.
+- Lombok `@Slf4j`, `@RequiredArgsConstructor`, `@Builder`, `@Data` are project standard.
+
+## Profiles
+
+| Profile | Port | DB | GCP auth | KMS | Logs |
+|---------|------|----|----------|-----|------|
+| `local` | 8091 | `10.2.7.23` hardcoded | creds file at `D:/SIPECOM/.../credentials_per.json` | **disabled** (payload read raw) | plain-text |
+| `dev` | 8080 | env vars | Workload Identity | enabled | plain-text |
+| `prod` | 8080 | env vars | Workload Identity | enabled | structured GCP JSON |
+
+## Build/deploy
+
+- **`build.sh`** uses **Podman** (not Docker) — pushes to `localhost:30500` with `--tls-verify=false`.
+- **Skaffold** (`v4beta11`): `skaffold.yaml` watches `src/` + `pom.xml`, custom build via `build.sh`.
+- Container base: `eclipse-temurin:25-jre`. Non-root user (`uid=10001`).
+- K8s manifests in `k8s/` — namespace `ns-cer-suite-dev`.
+
+## Test fixtures
+
+- `TslFrameParserServiceTest` has 3 embedded real TSLs: `TRAMA_TILL_CHANGE`, `TRAMA_CHECKOUT`, `TRAMA_CHECKOUT_CLIENTE`. Reuse these, don't create new raw strings.
+- Reference tramas in `.claude_analytics/tramas_tipo10.txt` (~3 MB production log).
+- **`.claude*` dirs are gitignored** — don't commit them.
+
+## Key gotchas
+
+- `--enable-preview` required at compile, test, AND runtime.
+- Amounts are raw cents — **never divide by 100** (ISSUE-01).
+- `99|06|41` UserData applies tax via FIFO queue per `itemCode` (ISSUE-V3-06).
+- XML amounts formatted as `"171.0"` (long + `.0`) — no decimal arithmetic.
+- `<IsPromo>` emitted only when `promoFlag` is non-null (`true`/`false`). Normal items omit the tag entirely.
+- README.md is a template stub — ignore it. Reference `CLAUDE.md` instead.


